-print\" onclick=\"addSpecialCondition()\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\">+ ADD SPECIAL CONDITION</button>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Section 9: Signature -->\n      <div class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"section-hd\"><div class=\"sec-num\">9</div><h2>ACCEPTANCE &amp; SIGNATURE</h2></div>\n        <div class=\"callout callout-gold\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\">\n          <strong>HOW TO ACCEPT:</strong> Option A — sign digitally in the box below and click \"Accept &amp; Sign\". Option B — print this page, sign, and return. In both cases, pay the booking deposit to confirm your start date.\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- CLIENT DIGITAL SIGNATURE -->\n        <div class=\"digital-sig-block\" id=\"q-digital-sig-block\">\n          <div class=\"digital-sig-title\">CLIENT DIGITAL SIGNATURE</div>\n          <div class=\"digital-sig-subtitle\">Draw your signature below using your mouse (desktop) or finger (mobile/tablet)</div>\n          <div class=\"sig-accepted-banner\" id=\"q-sig-accepted-banner\">\n            <img id=\"q-sig-image\" src=\"\" alt=\"Client Signature\" style=\"max-width:300px;margin-top:8px;display:none;\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"canvas-wrap\" id=\"q-canvas-wrap\">\n            <canvas id=\"q-sig-canvas\" width=\"757\" height=\"160\"></canvas>\n            <div class=\"canvas-hint\" id=\"q-canvas-hint\">SIGN HERE</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sig-btn-row\" id=\"q-sig-btn-row\">\n            <button class=\"sig-btn sig-btn-clear\" onclick=\"clearQuoteSig()\">CLEAR SIGNATURE</button>\n            <button class=\"sig-btn sig-btn-accept\" id=\"q-accept-btn\" onclick=\"acceptQuoteSig()\" disabled=\"\">ACCEPT &amp; SIGN</button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sig-fields-row\">\n            <div class=\"sig-field\">\n              <label class=\"sig-field-label\">FULL NAME</label>\n              <input type=\"text\" id=\"q-sig-typed-name\" class=\"sig-field-input sig-editable\" placeholder=\"Type client full name\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sig-field\">\n              <label class=\"sig-field-label\">PRINT NAME</label>\n              <input type=\"text\" id=\"q-sig-print-name\" class=\"sig-field-input sig-editable\" placeholder=\"Type client print name\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sig-field\">\n              <label class=\"sig-field-label\">DATE</label>\n              <input type=\"date\" id=\"q-sig-date\" class=\"sig-field-input sig-editable\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- RK AUTHORISED SIGNATURE -->\n        <div class=\"digital-sig-block\" id=\"q-rk-sig-block\" style=\"margin-top:24px;\">\n          <div class=\"digital-sig-title\">RENDER RENDER PTY LTD (RENDER KING) — AUTHORISED SIGNATORY</div>\n          <div class=\"digital-sig-subtitle\">King Mannion — Director</div>\n          <div class=\"sig-accepted-banner\" id=\"q-rk-sig-accepted-banner\">\n            <img id=\"q-rk-sig-image\" src=\"\" alt=\"RK Signature\" style=\"max-width:300px;margin-top:8px;display:none;\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"canvas-wrap\" id=\"q-rk-canvas-wrap\">\n            <canvas id=\"q-rk-sig-canvas\" width=\"757\" height=\"160\"></canvas>\n            <div class=\"canvas-hint\" id=\"q-rk-canvas-hint\">RK SIGN HERE</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sig-btn-row\" id=\"q-rk-sig-btn-row\">\n            <button class=\"sig-btn sig-btn-clear\" onclick=\"clearRkSig()\">CLEAR SIGNATURE</button>\n            <button class=\"sig-btn sig-btn-accept\" id=\"q-rk-accept-btn\" onclick=\"acceptRkSig()\" disabled=\"\">ACCEPT &amp; SIGN</button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"sig-fields-row\">\n            <div class=\"sig-field\">\n              <label class=\"sig-field-label\">NAME</label>\n              <input type=\"text\" id=\"q-rk-typed-name\" class=\"sig-field-input\" value=\"King Mannion\" readonly=\"\" style=\"color:var(--gold);\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sig-field\">\n              <label class=\"sig-field-label\">TITLE</label>\n              <input type=\"text\" id=\"q-rk-typed-title\" class=\"sig-field-input\" value=\"Director\" readonly=\"\" style=\"color:var(--gold);\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sig-field\">\n              <label class=\"sig-field-label\">DATE</label>\n              <input type=\"date\" id=\"q-rk-sig-date\" class=\"sig-field-input sig-editable\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div><!-- /doc-body -->\n\n    <div class=\"doc-footer\">\n      <div><span class=\"gold\">RENDER RENDER PTY LTD</span> — Trading as Render King</div>\n      <div>Phone: 0468 041 477 | Gold Coast, QLD</div>\n    </div>\n  "
